item.title: Fun at work
item.description: Today work is fun. well sorta. we got smoe good stuff done. but now I am ready to go home. Some friends and coworkers sent me some good links. Noel sent this gayness test in.. I am apparently 46% gay. wow surprise there huh ;) one of my coworkers sent this “Starship Dimensions” site to me. It is rather fun. Mostly because their are soooo many space ships.. This weekend made me(and my brother apparently) want a miniDV cam.
